00:13:43,900 --> 00:13:47,200
And I used to work a lot with him and interact with him
我经常和他一起工作 互动

254
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:52,900
and was constantly amazed by Warren
我经常为Warren折服

255
00:13:52,900 --> 00:13:58,800
Warren, at the time was 80 years old - now he's 83
Warren当时80岁 他现在83岁了

256
00:13:58,800 --> 00:14:03,600
would walk into the room and the room would light up
他走进教室时 整间教室都亮了起来

257
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:08,200
It was his smile, his posture, his openness
他的微笑 姿势 直率

258
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:11,400
his expressiveness
他丰富的表达

259
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:14,800
was there about his interacting with people
都是为了和同学发生互动

260
00:14:14,800 --> 00:14:17,900
and making the other person just by being there
他的一举一动让其他人

261
00:14:17,900 --> 00:14:21,100
feel better about themselves
对自己感觉更好了

262
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:24,700
And he was confident and strong
他自信坚强

263
00:14:24,700 --> 00:14:29,100
and what I would classify as self-actualized as a person
我把这样的人视为自我实现的人

264
00:14:29,100 --> 00:14:34,900
with very high unconditional self-esteem
他有很高的无条件自尊

265
00:14:34,900 --> 00:14:38,700
And we became very close and he helped me in many areas
我们走得很近 他在很多方面都给了我帮助

266
00:14:38,700 --> 00:14:42,700
most of all just by being himself - me observing him
最大的帮助就是他活出自我 我观察他

267
00:14:42,700 --> 00:14:48,000
learning from him, assimilating what he had to give the world
学习他 吸收他给这个世界带来的东西

