00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,100
and what he was giving day in and day out
吸收他每天给数百万读他的书的人

269
00:14:50,100 --> 00:14:52,900
to thousands and millions of people who have read his books
听他演讲的人

270
00:14:52,900 --> 00:14:54,600
who have been to his lectures
和他有过接触的人

271
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:59,000
who've had the privilege of interacting with him
所带来的知识

272
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:01,900
And one day after a couple of years
几年后 有一天

273
00:15:01,900 --> 00:15:03,700
I was his TA
我是他的助教

274
00:15:03,700 --> 00:15:05,400
and we were close
我们关系很亲近

275
00:15:05,400 --> 00:15:06,600
I said to him
我跟他说

