00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:12,700
"Warren, how is it that you are like this?"
"Warren 你是怎么变成现在这样的?"

277
00:15:12,700 --> 00:15:17,800
How is it that you are like this?
你是怎么变成现在这样的?

278
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:22,400
And his response was put his hand on my shoulder
他的回应时 把手放在我肩膀

279
00:15:22,400 --> 00:15:25,200
looked at me with his calm
看着我 带着一个平静

280
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:30,800
accepting, giving smile, and said
接受 慷慨的微笑 说

281
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:39,300
"Tal. I wasn't always like this"
"Tal 我不是一出生就这样的"

