00:15:39,300 --> 00:15:42,300
And that's where he left it
他就只说了这一句

283
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:46,100
And this is what I needed to hear
这就是我需要听到的答案

284
00:15:46,100 --> 00:15:48,400
Because in his response
因为在他的回答里

285
00:15:48,400 --> 00:15:51,100
where two very important - many more
有很多重要的信息

