00:15:51,100 --> 00:15:53,700
but two very important messages
而最重要的两个信息是

287
00:15:53,700 --> 00:15:57,600
the first message is that it evolves
第一个 他是慢慢进步成这样的

288
00:15:57,600 --> 00:16:03,400
it takes time; you don't become third level
需要时间 你不会在20岁时 或者40岁时

289
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:07,200
self-actualized individual overnight at the age of 20
一夜之间 去到第三层自尊

290
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:09,900
or even at the age of 40
变成一个自我实现的人

291
00:16:09,900 --> 00:16:14,500
It takes time; it takes work; it takes self-awareness
需要时间 需要下功夫

292
00:16:14,500 --> 00:16:16,500
it takes falling down and getting up
需要一次次跌倒和站起来

293
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:18,700
learning to fail
学会失败

294
00:16:18,700 --> 00:16:21,200
then learning from that failure
然后从失败中学习

295
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:23,200
It takes learning to accept oneself
需要学习接受自己

296
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:29,000
it takes being open and being vulnerable and making mistakes
需要敞开心扉 接受伤害 犯错

297
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:37,600
it takes being human, fully human
需要做一个彻彻底底的人

298
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:39,800
I was not always like this
我不是一出生就这样的

