我明白有高自尊的人都是谦虚的

316
00:17:25,700 --> 00:17:28,500
You don't have the need to show off
你不需要显摆

317
00:17:28,500 --> 00:17:29,600
You know, arrogance
你们知道 自大

318
00:17:29,600 --> 00:17:35,900
narcissism is the exact opposite of self-esteem
自恋是自尊的对立

319
00:17:35,900 --> 00:17:39,300
hubris, foolish pride is the exact opposite
目中无人 自以为是

320
00:17:39,300 --> 00:17:43,200
of what a true sense of self is
跟真正意义上的自我感是完全对立的

321
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:44,800
So when I understood that
所以当我明白了这点以后

322
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:50,000
one of my important goals was to become
我的一个重要目标就是变得

323
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:54,000
more importantly to be - modest
谦虚 最重要的目标

324
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:56,500
And it was incredibly important for me
所以我越来越觉得

325
00:17:56,500 --> 00:18:02,500
