这句话用在我身上最合适不过了

329
00:18:14,600 --> 00:18:16,500
it's not always the case
但对别人来说不总是这样

330
00:18:16,500 --> 00:18:20,800
I think Warren Bennis is modest and truly modest
我认为Warren Bennis是真正的谦虚

331
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:22,200
I think Nelson Mandela
我认为曼德拉

332
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:26,600
when he is being modest, he really is modest
当他谦虚时 他是真正的谦虚

333
00:18:26,600 --> 00:18:29,500
But the question is: how do you get to that level of modesty?
但问题是 你怎样才能达到那种层次的谦虚?

334
00:18:29,500 --> 00:18:32,300
