00:58:57,500 --> 00:59:03,800
that's when we identify the path that is right for me
我们才能找到适合我们的道路

1124
00:59:03,800 --> 00:59:07,200
Let me illustrate this by showing you a stage model
我想用一个阶段模型来给大家讲解

1125
00:59:07,200 --> 00:59:11,700
And this is based on the work of Daniel Gilbert
这是以Daniel Gilbert的研究为基础的

1126
00:59:11,700 --> 00:59:18,900
indirectly refers to it his work on cognitive dizziness
与他的认知晕眩研究有间接关系

