1155
01:00:40,000 --> 01:00:41,500
where we think about what we do
这时候我们会想我们做的事

1156
01:00:41,500 --> 01:00:45,600
we think about what we think
想我们想的事

1157
01:00:45,600 --> 01:00:48,600
We take our time
